<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</p><h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>COVID-19 UPDATES</strong></h1><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><strong>Last Updated January 6, 2021 at 12:30 PM</strong></p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">The Coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic is an evolving situation as we learn about the spread of infections and how best to address this public health crisis. I hope the following information and resources are helpful to you. Together, as a community, a Commonwealth, and a nation, we are facing a truly unprecedented situation. The global coronavirus pandemic is affecting all of our families, our houses of worship, charities and businesses, our communities—our very way of life. </p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">During this time, I want to let you know that your elected leaders are working tirelessly together to keep open our channels of communication. Keeping residents of the 44th district informed during this time is a priority for me. I will be monitoring this situation daily as changes take place and will keep you up to date. <strong>Please follow my Twitter updates </strong><a href="https://twitter.com/KrizekForVA">here</a><strong> and follow my Facebook updates </strong><a href="https://www.facebook.com/KrizekForVA/">here.</a><strong> </strong></p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p>
